    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A colorless, liquid hydrocarbon obtained in the fractional distillation of petroleum which is used chiefly as a motor fuel but also as a solvent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
